  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the sea bass fillets with salt, black pepper, and thyme.",
    "Heat the olive oil in an oven safe skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Sear the sea bass fillets for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Add the seafood stock, garlic, and lemon juice to the skillet.",
    "Transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and roast for 12 minutes.",
    "Remove the skillet from the oven and let the fish rest for 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the fish hot, garnished with fresh thyme and lemon wedges."
